title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 §§ 151-1.3 - Supporting memorandum
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 §§ 151-1.3 - Supporting memorandum

State Regulations

Each workers' compensation rate filing with a rate impact shall be supported by a memorandum that contains a comparison between any existing filing and the proposed revision describing and justifying all changes. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11
§§
151-1.3

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
